'''Sap''' is a [[:Category:Foraging|foraged]] item that drops from [[trees]] when they are cut down. It is used in various [[crafting]] recipes. Sap can be consumed, however it decreases [[energy]] by 2 points.

Sap may also be obtained from tapping [[Mahogany Tree]]s and all [[Slimes]] except [[Slimes#Big Slimes|Big Slimes]].

