==Bundles==
Sap is used in the {{Bundle|Sticky||y}}.

==Tailoring==
Sap is used in the spool of the [[2 Willow Lane#Sewing Machine|Sewing Machine]] with [[Cloth]] in the feed to create a {{name|Shirt006|link=Tailoring{{!}}Tan Striped Shirt|class=inline}}. It is a yellow dye when used in the spool of the Sewing Machine with a dyeable clothing item in the feed. It can be placed in the yellow dye pot at Emily's and Haley's house for use in [[dyeing]].

==Quests==
Sap is not used in any [[Quests|quests]].

==Bugs==
While playing local co-op on console, if the player or a farmhand has had [[Energy|exhaustion]] the previous day and consumes a poisonous item that reduces their energy to zero (or below), the game will softlock.

